snippet.title: SWORD ART ONLINE Fractured Daydream — Eiji & Yuna Trailer
snippet.description:
A love that transcends life and cyberspace. Eiji and Yuna slash and sing into battle!

SWORD ART ONLINE Fractured Daydream comes to PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X|S, Nintendo Switch, and Steam on October 4th, 2024.

Pre-order today to receive the Demon King Costume Set for Kirito: https://bnent.eu/PreorderSAOFD 

Purchase the Digital Deluxe Edition to receive the Prism Heart Costume Set, Character Pass Vol.1, and 3 days early access!
Purchase the Digital Premium to receive everything from the Deluxe edition plus the Wild Joke Dress and Digital Artbook and Soundtrack!

Worlds collide. Heroes unite.
SWORD ART ONLINE characters from across time and cyberspace team up in 20-player raiding parties to face powerful enemies. Choose your character, gather your allies, and push forward to victory!

#SWORDARTONLINE #FracturedDaydream
Follow Sword Art Games:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/saogames
